title: Itcooking.eu - IP Geolocation

api_list.name: /geoip/v1/lite/GetIpInfoLiteBatch
api_list.description: Batch identification of location for max 16 IP address per request.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://itcooking-eu-ip-geolocation1.p.rapidapi.com/geoip/v1/lite/GetIpInfoLiteBatch"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "itcooking-eu-ip-geolocation1.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
